# Locally fetched model weights (multi-GB) — never commit these.
# scripts/fetch-bonsai-gguf.sh downloads + verifies them on demand, and the
# offline image bake stages a pre-fetched GGUF here. Keep the directory itself
# (via .keep) so Dockerfile.llamacpp's `COPY deploy/ollama/models/` works on a
# clean checkout, but never commit the weights.
models/*
!models/.keep
*.gguf
